---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContactButton from '../components/buttons/ContactButton.astro'; 
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | GBRS Services | Hartlepool Construction"
  description="About GBRS Services - Family-run construction business in Hartlepool. Meet our team and learn about 40+ years experience in agricultural and industrial building."
  activePage="about"
>
  <section class="page-hero" id="main">
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <h1>About GBRS Services</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Family-Run Excellence Since 1980</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">Our Story</span>
          <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="lead-text">
          <strong>GBRS Services Ltd</strong> is a trusted, family-run construction business proudly serving 
          <strong>Hartlepool, County Durham, and the wider North East</strong>. 
        </p>
        <p>
          With over <strong>40 years of combined hands-on experience</strong>, we handle every stage of your 
          construction project from initial groundworks to final finishes - Hence 'Foundations to Finish'.
        </p>

        <p>Our reputation is built 
          on quality workmanship, reliability, and personal service that only a family business can provide.
        </p>
        <p>
          We specialise in <strong>Agricultural and Industrial Construction Services</strong>, offering comprehensive 
          services including Groundworks, Foundations, Steel Erection, Sheeting and cladding, and Civil engineering works.  
          Everything is handled in-house by our skilled team no subcontractors, just honest, hard-working 
          professionals who take pride in their craft.
        </p>
        
        <div class="about-features">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h3>40+ Years Experience</h3>
              <p>Proven expertise in agricultural & industrial construction across the North East</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Family-Run Business</h3>
              <p>Personal service and attention to every project, big or small</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Complete In-House</h3>
              <p>All work done by our skilled team, no subcontractors</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Local to North East</h3>
              <p>Based in Hartlepool, serving County Durham, Teesside & beyond</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="team section" style="background: white;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Meet the Team</span>
        <h2>The People Behind GBRS</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="services-intro">
        Our family-run team brings decades of combined experience in construction tailored to the Agricultural and Industrial Sectors. 
        We're dedicated to delivering quality results and excellent customer service on every project.
      </p>

      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-placeholder">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--primary)" width="80" height="80">
              <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="team-content">
            <h3>George Bell</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Founder & Managing Director</p>
            <p class="team-bio">
              GBRS Services continues the trusted legacy of the Bell family.
              Building on decades of experience, George has continued to maintain the same commitment to quality, reliability, and craftsmanship that customers across the North East have come to trust.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-placeholder">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--primary)" width="80" height="80">
              <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="team-content">
            <h3>George Bell Snr</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Consultant & industry veteran</p>
            <p class="team-bio">
              Now taking the back seat, his son, George continues to share his expertise and guidance, ensuring the company's strong principles remain at the heart of every project.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-placeholder">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--primary)" width="80" height="80">
              <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="team-content">
            <h3>The GBRS Team</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Skilled Workforce</p>
            <p class="team-bio">
              The GBRS team is made up of trusted, professionals many of whom have worked with the Bell family for years. 
              With between 10 and 30 years of experience across steel erection, groundworks, and general construction, our team continues to deliver the same trusted craftsmanship and reliability that have defined the Bell name for decades.
              Together, they support GBRS into the next generation of family-led construction excellence.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values section" style="background: var(--light-grey);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Our Values</span>
        <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Quality Workmanship</h3>
          <p>
            We take pride in every project, ensuring the highest standards of workmanship 
            from foundations to finish. Our reputation is built on quality that lasts.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Reliability & Honesty</h3>
          <p>
            When we say we'll be there, we'll be there. Transparent pricing, honest advice, 
            and reliable service you can count on.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Customer Focus</h3>
          <p>
            Your project is our priority. We listen to your needs, provide expert guidance, 
            and deliver solutions that exceed expectations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Local Expertise</h3>
          <p>
            Based in Hartlepool with deep roots in the North East, we understand local 
            building requirements and serve our community with pride.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section section" style="background: white; text-align: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #111;">Ready to Start Your Project?</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #555; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        Get in touch today for a free, no-obligation quote. We're here to help bring your construction project to life.
      </p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <ContactButton btnText="Get a Quote" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
